    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……哈啊……\\n也不在这里……\\n安洁……究竟跑哪去了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "哟，戈尔德。\\n找到你亲爱的小安洁了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "拜莱德？\\n我现在没空理你。快滚。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "你对我这种态度合适吗？\\n不想见你可爱的孙女了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "拜莱德……你这家伙，\\n对安洁做了什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "呵呵呵……别那么生气嘛。\\n我只是把她请到了我家里\\n做客而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "你掳走了安洁吗！\\n混账，你竟敢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "噫……这魄力还真是吓人。\\n不过话别说得那么难听。我只是帮你\\n把离家出走的孙女保护起来了而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "为了那小姑娘的人身安全，\\n你就老实听话吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "呃……让我见见安洁。\\n拜托了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "呵呵呵……既然是你的请求，\\n我也不好不听……\\n不过你也得听我一个请求才行。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "回来吧，戈尔德。\\n回“恶刚会”辅佐我吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "为什么……非我不可？\\n我都已经把“恶刚会”的领袖之位\\n让给了你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "事到如今，\\n应该没有我的事了吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "会这么想的只有你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "不管是谁，只要发生一点问题\\n就会说“要是戈尔德在”这种话。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "所以我必须让那些人\\n看到你臣服于我的样子！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "……\\n我明白了……就听你的吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "呵呵呵……\\n没错，只要你乖乖听话，\\n就不会牵连任何人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "哈哈哈哈！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "呜、呜呜呜……呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "爷、爷爷！\\n啊、不对……\\n不是……我的爷爷……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "安洁……都是我不好。\\n但我不是有意骗你的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "我本想，等你长大一点\\n再跟你坦白……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "但我……还是希望你能告诉我……\\n明明是我自己的事，\\n我却完全不了解……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "嗯……是啊。你说得对。\\n等你长大再说，这只是借口。\\n其实是因为我害怕……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "害怕？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "要是跟你坦白了一切，\\n你会怎么想……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "我一直在担心……\\n那样一来你是不是就\\n再也不肯叫我爷爷了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "因为我的懦弱，\\n让你受到了伤害……\\n我真的觉得很抱歉。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "希望你能原谅我。\\n然后，如果你愿意，\\n能不能再叫我一声爷爷……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "诶。啊……爷——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "打住。令人感动的\\n重逢戏码就到此为止吧。\\n小姑娘你过来这边。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "呀啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "拜莱德，你要把安洁带去哪里！\\n你要是敢对她动粗，\\n我绝对饶不了你！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "给我闭嘴，戈尔德！\\n发号施令的是我！你只能服从！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "呀！啊、啊啊……\\n啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "不好，又发病了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "拜莱德，算我求你。\\n别在这孩子面前动粗。\\n我都这样求你了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "哈哈哈哈！这感觉太棒了！\\n传说中的“赤臂戈尔德”\\n在低声下气地求我！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "很好，很好。如果你真的在乎她，\\n就乖乖地听我的命令，懂吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "好、好吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "总之你先老老实实\\n给我在这房间里待着。\\n可别打什么逃跑的鬼主意。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "拜莱德",
            "context": "放心，很快就会放你出去的。\\n毕竟我有很多工作\\n需要你去做呢。呵呵呵……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "安洁……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "当天晚上——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "安洁，对不起。都怪我，\\n让你受怕了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "我不能再让安洁\\n担惊受怕了。哪怕……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "哪怕，染指恶行吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "你是……“狩人者”！\\n为什么……会在这里？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "之前就说了，\\n我想阻止“恶刚会”的暴行。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "你是想杀了拜莱德吗……\\n不，你的目标也包括我吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "如果有那个必要……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "或许拜莱德成为你的目标\\n是无可奈何的……\\n但现在能不能先放他一马！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "你是指那个叫安洁的小姑娘吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "你都知道吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "嗯，我以前也见过类似的人。\\n她看上去受了很严重的\\n心灵创伤啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "这都怪我……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "安洁的亲生父亲叫基亚尔德，\\n曾经也是“恶刚会”的一员。\\n说实话，他不是个好东西。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "他借着“恶刚会”的名号四处逞威风，\\n情况不对就跑路。从来不信守承诺，\\n什么事都只考虑自己。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "不过原本“恶刚会”就是作为\\n这类人的归宿而建立的。\\n所以多少会有一些无可救药的家伙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "但那家伙……\\n做了绝对不该做的事。他把同伴……\\n把“恶刚会”的同伴杀了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "不仅如此，基亚尔德还因为\\n害怕遭到报复而投奔敌对组织，\\n出卖了“恶刚会”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "我作为领袖，自然不能放过他。\\n最终，我揪出了基亚尔德……\\n清理了门户。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "刚好被看到了吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "是的。那孩子……\\n安洁目睹了他父亲的鲜血\\n染红我手臂的那一幕……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "当时还在襁褓中的安洁，\\n不可能记得这一切。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "但是……自那以后\\n安洁还是变得异常恐惧暴力，\\n遇到那种场面就会发病。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "我……小时候活得很不容易。\\n被不负责任的父母抛弃，\\n只能靠自己活下去……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "一群类似的混混小鬼们\\n为了拥有自己的容身之处\\n才创立了“恶刚会”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "然而不知不觉间，\\n却成了致使孩子们\\n不幸的那一方。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "察觉到这个事实之后，\\n我再也无法继续\\n待在“恶刚会”了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "所以你才舍弃了“赤臂”吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "嗯……因为我需要的\\n并不是“赤臂”，\\n而是能拥抱孩子们的手。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "但那也许只是一种逃避。\\n舍弃“赤臂”和“恶刚会”，\\n都只是在逃避而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "或许我该做的不是舍弃“赤臂”，\\n而是用它来纠正“恶刚会”的错……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "我一路走来都在犯错啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "犯了错只要改正就好。\\n现在还为时未晚。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "呼……没想到我竟然\\n会被“狩人者”安慰啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "正因为我被称为“狩人者”，\\n所以才渴望安稳幸福的世界。\\n毕竟我自己无法得到这一切。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "这算是同病相怜吗……\\n不过你说得没错，\\n现在改正也还来得及。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "“狩人者”，能不能帮帮我？\\n我必须去找安洁和拜莱德。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍克",
            "context": "行。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "等着我，安洁！\\n我这就来！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}